Dear Mr. Shohaib 

 

We are writing to formally discontinue our agreement for recruitment
services, effective immediately.

 

Unfortunately, we have been consistently disappointed with the results of
your recruitment efforts. 

 

The candidates provided have not met our expectations, and we have not been
able to successfully fill our open positions. We feel that the quality of
candidates and your understanding of our requirements has not been up to the
standard we need.

 

We appreciate the time you have spent trying to help us

 


Thanks & Regards,


Ankesh Pal

